entries.content:
Lady Gaga tweeted today that all the fashion credit for her Monster's Ball tour goes to Nichola Formichetti.  It took more than 20 minutes for me to pick one fabulous thing to blog about out of all the goodies posted on his blog.  Do yourself a favor and watch those vids over lunch.

I don't recall hearing any songs about a Hair Monster on her record, though...

entries.content:
from fuckyeadaria.tumblr.com


I loved Daria's credits as much as I loved the show.  Wikipedia even noticed!

After each episode, credits would roll on one half of the screen, and the other would display series characters drawn out of character (termed by fans as "alter egos"). They ranged from Tiffany as a Pokémon, to Quinn's constant followers (Joey, Jeffy, and Jamie) as the three main characters from the movie O Brother, Where Art Thou?, to Jane as the Statue of Liberty.

There should be a Daria Appreciation week.
